280
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:10,780
<i>Greetings, Your Supreme Majesty, Your Majesty.</i>

281
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:15,880
Emperor Ying Yuan you are extremely powerful.

282
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:18,359
