283
00:32:18,359 --> 00:32:21,300
Do not worry, Marshal. I'm all right.

284
00:32:21,300 --> 00:32:23,180
I'm glad to hear that.

285
00:32:23,180 --> 00:32:24,659
So what is happening?

286
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:31,339
